<P>
<PRE><B>1902</B>  Theodor Mommsen            Germany</PRE>
<P>
<PRE><B>1901</B>  Sully Prudhomme            France</PRE>
<P>
<PRE><B>    </B>  Rene Francois Armand       France</PRE>

