( in millions of dollars )

<P>

<P>New York / $283.2
<P>Northern California / $280.1
<P>Los Angeles / $265.6
<P>Boston / $168.8
<P>Chicago / $162.8
<P>Washington D.C / $148.4

<BR><BR><BR>

