<P><img width=580 height=534 border=2 src="image/applyB.gif" alt="form2"></CENTER>

<P>

<CENTER><P><FONT SIZE=+1><B>Thank you for your interest. 

<P>Please print out this page and return your completed application and enclosed check to: 

<P>Northern California Independent Booksellers Association, 5643 Paradise Drive. # 12, Corte Madera,  California 94925</B></FONT></CENTER>

