<DOCOLDNO>IA070-000437-B013-194</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://gardnerweb.com:80/pf/pf_articles/079603.html 206.112.192.204 19970120211029 text/html 8396
HTTP/1.0 200 OK
Date: Mon, 20 Jan 1997 21:10:26 GMT
