Edge Coverage,&quot; John A. Gilbert, BASF Corporation; &quot;Environmentally Driven Zinc Phosphate Technology,&quot; Sherif Rabbah, Oakite Products; &quot;Submersible Data Acquisition Unit for Electrodeposition Tanks,&quot; Joseph J. Subda, DuPont; &quot;Electrocoating Tube-and-Fin Heat Exchangers,&quot; Jeff Oravitz, PPG Industries; and &quot;New Developments in Material Handling Systems for Electrocoating,&quot; Ari Lehman, Nichidai Industries. <P>
<B>1:00 - 3:30 p.m.</B><BR> 
End-User Information Exchange.<BR> 
