<HTML>

<HEAD><TITLE>Products Finishing, September 96, "Self-Assessment Tool for Finishers"
</TITLE>
<CONTENT="September 1996, Products Finishing">
</HEAD>

<A NAME="top">

<BODY>
<A NAME="top">
