Sons, England. <BR>
<BR>
<B>Graetz, R. D., Wilson, M. A., and Campbell, S. K.</B>, 1995. <I>Landcover
disturbance over the Australian continent: A contemporary assessment. Biodiversity
Series Paper No. 7</I>, Biodiversity Unit, Department of the Environment,
Sport &amp; Territories, Canberra. <BR>
