COSSA Slides 438 - 453 <BR>
depict images from NASA's Ocean Zone Colour Scanner<BR>
&quot;Ocean Colour from Space&quot; pamphlet.<BR>
(Courtesy:  Gene Feldman, NASA Goddard Space Flight Centre).<BR>
