OUR APPROACH<BR>
Duplex soils (Dr 2.12) have formed in granodiorite in the Upper Burdekin
River Catchment.  Red subsoils, exposed to erosion of ridge tops, can be
detected on Landsat TM imagery (30m pixels).<BR>
